articles.title: Volcano Erupts In Guatemala, Forcing Closure Of Airport, Highway - NDTV
articles.description: One of the most active volcanoes in Central America has erupted again, spewing lava and ash and forcing authorities in Guatemala City on Sunday to briefly close the country's largest airport and a major highway.
articles.content:
